summary: I once had this really weird dream in which I was at (in that moment) my guy’s house getting married to Chris Evans, apparently...
body: I once had this really weird dream in which I was at (in that moment) my guy’s house getting married to Chris Evans, apparently the reception was there, but here is where it gets weird, there was this HUGE glass shower in the living room and I was inside it with my soon to be husband NAKED and my whole family + friends and said guy l were all looking at us, acting like if that wasn’t weird at all. And I remember telling Chris “hey why are we showering here? Everyone can see us” and he said something along the lines of “don’t worry about it” and people kept walking in from the door at our right. I woke up confused but certain that I was, in fact, Chris Evans’ wife. Also I should add that we were speaking English, which is not my first lengauage and Chris Evans was dry and kind of cold????? Also he was kinda short

Chris in Boston, Massachusetts with his family when his uncle Mike Capuano was running for congress.
